    <custom_item>
      type        : CMD_EXEC
      description : "5.1.1 Secure Home Folders"
      info        : "By default macOS allows all valid users into the top level of every other users home folder, and restricts access to the Apple default folders within. Another user on the same system can see you have a 'Documents' folder but cannot see inside it. This configuration does work for personal file sharing but can expose user files to standard accounts on the system.

